outline: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: currentcolor;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px !important;"><div data-darkmode-bgcolor-16095509242984="rgb(25, 25, 25)" data-darkmode-original-bgcolor-16095509242984="rgb(255, 255, 255)" data-style="margin-top: 2em; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; border-style: solid none; text-decoration: inherit; border-top-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-bottom-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" mp-original-font-size="17" mp-original-line-height="27.200000762939453" style="margin-top: 2em;padding-top: 0.5em;padding-bottom: 0.5em;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);border-top: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);border-right-style: none;border-left-style: none;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px !important;"><p style="margin-top: -1.2em;outline: 0px;text-align: center;font-family: inherit;border-width: initial;border-style: initial;border-color: currentcolor;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(163, 163, 163) !important;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: inherit;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(117, 117, 118);text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;line-height: 29.75px;">机器之心报道</span></p><p style="outline: 0px;text-align: center;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;visibility: visible;"><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;">编辑：杜伟</strong></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><blockquote class="js_blockquote_wrap" data-type="2" data-url="" data-author-name="" data-content-utf8-length="38" data-source-title=""><div class="js_blockquote_digest"><p style="line-height: 1.75em;">以后的视频生成领域，恐怕真的只有 OpenAI 的 Sora 和其他模型了。</p></div></blockquote><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">昨天，OpenAI 发布的首个文本生成视频模型 Sora 引爆了社区，其生成的长达 1 分钟的高清、流畅视频令人们惊叹不已，直呼「好莱坞的时代结束了」。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p><iframe class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-vidtype="2" data-mpvid="wxv_3329686113287913473" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagkmJtFlaIs2ucNcfkl3QmPRicYjVjyAKPn19Tiag9G8YmYpHgJv4tUUoA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-w="1920" style="border-radius: 4px;" data-src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3329686113287913473"></iframe></p><p><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">仅仅一年时间，文本生成视频的效果迎来了质的飞跃。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="503424074" data-ratio="0.6203703703703703" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="648" style="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gWibxlIj3fpKic64KUSUc6miavnaibpiadup4vWMO1DwotAxJltxDBSX9l7HendYj8MaicBMeNyllYnxZIaA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em><span style="font-size: 12px;">图源：https://twitter.com/samsheffer/status/1758205467682357732</span></em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">当然，随着 Sora 加入这场视频生成领域的战争，受到冲击最大的是同类竞品模型，比如 Runway、Pika、SDV、谷歌和 Meta。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">看到 Sora 的生成效果之后，很多人认为，Sora 对这些「前辈」来了一波降维打击。事实真的如此吗？有推特博主已经做了对比。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="503424107" data-ratio="0.4119278779472954" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="721" style="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gWibxlIj3fpKic64KUSUc6miavnYkbuNvSlNZsuwgFTNCMf3W5JNexFnyPN20OKq34EBREFVqFK1mFISg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"></span></p><p><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">这位博主给 Sora、Pika、Runway、Stable Video 四个模型输入了相同的 prompt：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br></span></p><blockquote class="js_blockquote_wrap" data-type="2" data-url="" data-author-name="" data-content-utf8-length="67" data-source-title=""><div class="js_blockquote_digest"><div><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">美丽、白雪皑皑的东京熙熙攘攘，镜头穿过熙熙攘攘的城市街道，跟随几个人享受美丽的雪天，在附近的摊位购物，绚丽的樱花花瓣随着雪花随风飘扬。</span></p></div></div></blockquote><p><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">可以看到，相比于其他三个视频生成模型，Sora 在生成时长、连贯性等方面都有显著的优势。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="503424075" data-ratio="0.5416666666666666" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="696" style="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gWibxlIj3fpKic64KUSUc6miavnWFmZxJJNkCqiakrnYIC2f2V2moxJyZyJm2KZiarafc9a8g8icZ0IKy9qQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;"><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span>图源：https://twitter.com/gabor/status/1758282791547232482</span></em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">这样的对比还有很多，比如输入相同的 prompt「一窝金毛幼犬在雪地里玩耍，它们的头从雪中探出来，被雪覆盖。」</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="503424076" data-ratio="0.9826254826254827" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="518" style="width: 578px;height: 568px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gWibxlIj3fpKic64KUSUc6miavn6CjcE3nLZ1ZozUkIExiarhzkSQIc8K9G65emNuTJpfLFFvoJzxt6HeQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em><span style="font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">图源：https://twitter.com/DailyUpdatesNet/status/1758646902751670355</span></em></span><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">再比如输入相同的 prompt「几只巨大的毛茸茸的猛犸象踏着白雪皑皑的草地走来，长长的毛毛在风中轻轻飘动，远处覆盖着积雪的树木和雄伟的雪山，午后的阳光、缕缕云彩和远处高高的太阳营造出温暖的光芒，低相机视野令人惊叹地捕捉到了大型毛茸茸的哺乳动物与美丽的摄影，景深。」</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">虽然 Runway 和 Pika 表现都不错，但 Sora 的生成质量具有压倒性的优势。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="503424077" data-ratio="0.5398089171974523" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="628" style="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gWibxlIj3fpKic64KUSUc6miavnn16NBxd5aOI5XXB2InPQIX6F8oKAgqtqL0bkmOtmvw4WwvDoLq8eUw/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em><span style="font-size: 12px;">图源：https://twitter.com/keitowebai/status/1758384152670577136</span></em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">还有人对比了 Pika 1.0（去年四月）与 Sora，感叹不到 1 年的时间，AI 生成视频已经发生了翻天覆地的变化。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p><iframe class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-vidtype="2" data-mpvid="wxv_3331024425332228104" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gWibxlIj3fpKic64KUSUc6miavn7Ee7oK2cWe5HyRfmn4RAPPQkysibXrthZ1xt4nFgB81icoohPvbvhQUw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-w="1280" style="border-radius: 4px;" data-src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3331024425332228104"></iframe></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em><span style="font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">原视频：https://twitter.com/QuintinAu/status/1758536835595124910</span></em></span><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">与此同时，更多创作者也晒出了他们使用 Sora 生成的视频，进一步验证了 Sora 的超强视频生成能力。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">比如输入 prompt「一座巨大的大教堂里全是猫。放眼望去，到处都是猫。一个男人走进大教堂，向坐在王座上的巨型猫王鞠躬。」</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="503424078" data-ratio="0.5333333333333333" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="555" style="width: 578px;height: 308px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gWibxlIj3fpKic64KUSUc6miavn3qzY5RNtI6cuuA2bpN4dgJorIxu3uhk80zyXGE8aQVeBB2UIjpScNA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;"></span></span></em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em><span style="font-size: 12px;">图源：https://twitter.com/billpeeb/status/1758650919430848991</span></em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">比如输入 prompt「一座幽灵般的鬼屋，有友好的杰克灯笼和鬼魂人物，欢迎捣蛋鬼来到入口，倾斜移位摄影。」</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="503424079" data-ratio="0.9980769230769231" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="520" style="width: 578px;height: 577px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gWibxlIj3fpKic64KUSUc6miavnUYCESZyOhO1lGgHhCD4VyMCmpJDDblLq0eSHWBMbNEC3bZffoqL3icQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;">图源：https://twitter.com/billpeeb/status/1758658884582142310</span></em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">比如输入 prompt「一个由水制成的人行走着，参观了一个美术馆，里面有许多不同风格的美丽艺术品。」</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="503424080" data-ratio="0.5384615384615384" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="520" style="width: 578px;height: 311px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gWibxlIj3fpKic64KUSUc6miavn8oViaksbOKTr1AbC34cj6Oia9kJSQI140ueqr2Lv3IqMTZzTxS8bZichA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;">图源：https://twitter.com/_tim_brooks/status/1758666264032280683</span></em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">比如输入 prompt「人们在海滩放松的真实视频，一条鲨鱼从水中冒了出来，让所有人大吃一惊。」</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="503424081" data-ratio="0.5365384615384615" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="520" style="width: 578px;height: 310px;display: inline;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gWibxlIj3fpKic64KUSUc6miavnRTf7zeKxibuibq7AaF7VvGQwNp2Qp79EIujMr23PgImq4zHdmbHglSHw/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><em><span style="font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><span style="display: none;line-height: 0px;">‍</span>图源：https://twitter.com/_tim_brooks/status/1758655323576164830</span></em></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">在 Sora 震撼效果的背后，OpenAI 也于昨日公布了详细的技术报告。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="503424082" data-ratio="0.4046296296296296" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gWibxlIj3fpKic64KUSUc6miavnicKS5WZgO2WcGGj5ScmmZHqp9MBuBpdPmJSuewWuOCSjLjsltjib7iaIg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"></span></p><p><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">技术报告地址 https://openai.com/research/video-generation-models-as-world-simulators</span><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">Sora 背后的技术</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">OpenAI 在技术报告中重点展示了：（1）将所有类型的视觉数据转化为统一表示，从而能够大规模训练生成模型的方法；以及（2）对 Sora 的能力和局限性进行定性评估。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">令人遗憾的是，OpenAI 的报告不包含模型和训练的细节。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">最近一段时间，视频生成是 AI 领域的重要方向，先前的许多工作研究了视频数据的生成建模方向，包括循环网络、生成对抗网络、自回归 transformer 和扩散模型。这些工作通常关注一小类视觉数据、较短的视频或固定大小的视频。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">与之不同的是，OpenAI 的 Sora 是视觉数据的通用模型，它可以生成不同时长、长宽比和分辨率的视频和图像，而且最多可以输出长达一分钟的高清视频。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;">视觉数据转为 Patches</strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">大型语言模型通过在互联网规模的数据上进行训练，获得了出色的通用能力中，OpenAI 从这一点汲取了灵感。LLM 得以确立新范式，部分得益于创新了 token 使用的方法。研究人员们巧妙地将文本的多种模态 —— 代码、数学和各种自然语言统一了起来。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">在这项工作中，OpenAI 考虑了生成视觉数据的模型如何继承这种方法的好处。大型语言模型有文本 token，而 Sora 有视觉 patches。此前的研究已经证明 patches 是视觉数据模型的有效表示。OpenAI 发现 patches 是训练生成各种类型视频和图像的模型的可扩展且有效的表示。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="503424083" data-ratio="0.18611111111111112" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagD6bibv5ssITGhiaA2F7UWK6xJiatnROS8L2gu88VguDplf5RpKWca2LWA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">在更高层面上，OpenAI 首先将视频压缩到较低维的潜在空间，然后将表示分解为时空 patches，从而将视频转换为 patches。</span><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;">视频压缩网络</strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">OpenAI 训练了一个降低视觉数据维度的网络。该网络将原始视频作为输入，并输出在时间和空间上压缩的潜在表示。Sora 在这个压缩的潜在空间中接受训练，而后生成视频。OpenAI 还训练了相应的解码器模型，将生成的潜在表示映射回像素空间。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;">时空潜在 patches</strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">给定一个压缩的输入视频，OpenAI 提取一系列时空 patches，充当 Transformer 的 tokens。该方案也适用于图像，因为图像可视为单帧视频。OpenAI 基于 patches 的表示使 Sora 能够对不同分辨率、持续时间和长宽比的视频和图像进行训练。在推理时，OpenAI 可以通过在适当大小的网格中排列随机初始化的 patches 来控制生成视频的大小。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;">用于视频生成的缩放 Transformer</strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">Sora 是个扩散模型；给定输入噪声 patches（以及文本提示等调节信息），训练出的模型来预测原始的「干净」patches。重要的是，Sora 是一个扩散 Transformer。Transformer 在各个领域都表现出了卓越的缩放特性，包括语言建模、计算机视觉、和图像生成。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="503424084" data-ratio="0.24722222222222223" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagbqkK5eBnicmWBuNK1pPgdqxE9TYmOUhpvNE9HMRvIASfhL7FUyMPAlw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">在这项工作中，OpenAI 发现扩散 Transformers 也可以有效地缩放为视频模型。下面，OpenAI 展示了训练过程中具有固定种子和输入的视频样本的比较。随着训练计算的增加，样本质量显着提高。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="503424087" data-ratio="0.4166666666666667" data-type="gif" data-w="600" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 600px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagoHR1hP4N6C94JzWF6wzpYakzS7muAeAsBHGjmPaUvjRZWa9KiaGMpkw/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;">可变的持续时间，分辨率，宽高比</strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">过去的图像和视频生成方法通常需要调整大小、进行裁剪或者是将视频剪切到标准尺寸，例如 4 秒的视频分辨率为 256x256。相反，该研究发现在原始大小的数据上进行训练，可以提供以下好处：</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">首先是采样的灵活性：</span><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">Sora 可以采样宽屏视频 1920x1080p，垂直视频 1920x1080p 以及两者之间的视频。</span><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">这使 Sora 可以直接以其天然纵横比为不同设备创建内容。</span><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">Sora 还允许在生成全分辨率的内容之前，以较小的尺寸快速创建内容原型 —— 所有内容都使用相同的模型。</span><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="503424086" data-ratio="0.29313543599257885" data-type="gif" data-w="1078" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagemj00iaIza8sJu7vMCehTASRS1zO9EvK912OVcG0icJmqx566ma0xiaUg/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">其次是改进帧和内容组成：研究者通过实证发现，使用视频的原始长宽比进行训练可以提升内容组成和帧的质量。将 Sora 在与其他模型的比较中，后者将所有训练视频裁剪成正方形，这是训练生成模型时的常见做法。经过正方形裁剪训练的模型（左侧）生成的视频，其中的视频主题只是部分可见。相比之下，Sora 生成的视频（右侧）具有改进的帧内容。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="503424085" data-ratio="0.4765625" data-type="gif" data-w="640" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 640px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagYhZVa75j1E3KCQY1aawkMe2OGFyk4fkibb3wvbQHPZV9OM6nDKT8JGw/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;">语言理解</strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">训练文本到视频生成系统需要大量带有相应文本字幕的视频。研究团队将 DALL・E 3 中的重字幕（re-captioning）技术应用于视频。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">具体来说，研究团队首先训练一个高度描述性的字幕生成器模型，然后使用它为训练集中所有视频生成文本字幕。研究团队发现，对高度描述性视频字幕进行训练可以提高文本保真度以及视频的整体质量。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">与 DALL・E 3 类似，研究团队还利用 GPT 将简短的用户 prompt 转换为较长的详细字幕，然后发送到视频模型。这使得 Sora 能够生成准确遵循用户 prompt 的高质量视频。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;">以图像和视频作为提示</strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">我们已经看到了文本到视频的诸多生成示例。实际上，Sora 还可以使用其他输入，如已有的图像或视频。这使 Sora 能够执行各种图像和视频编辑任务 — 创建完美的循环视频、静态图像动画、向前或向后延长视频时间等。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">为 DALL-E 图像制作动画</span><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"></span></strong><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">只要输入图像和提示，Sora 就能生成视频。下面展示了根据 DALL-E 2 和 DALL-E 3 图像生成的视频示例：</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="503424088" data-ratio="0.4765625" data-type="gif" data-w="640" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 640px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagpoia57EeVeeKz045IdUKV6Mr4VXtlqXagaRdxXZZjJfnte13JzymECA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em style="outline: 0px;">狗戴着贝雷帽、穿着黑色高领毛衣</em></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: 