t YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">视频内容拓展</span><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></strong><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">Sora 还能够在开头或结尾扩展视频内容。以下是 Sora 从一段生成的视频向后拓展出的三个新视频。新视频的开头各不相同，拥有相同的结尾。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p><iframe class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-w="1080" data-ratio="0.5927552140504939" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagiajjicEWByyhhlmWmnKwUSia08VRNtZGCpXcDgpX4BLARpOrp1rSNticxw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-mpvid="wxv_3329685928168112134" data-vidtype="2" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" style="border-radius: 4px;" data-src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3329685928168112134"></iframe></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">不妨使用这种方法无限延长视频的内容，实现「视频制作永动机」。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="503424090" data-ratio="0.5625" data-type="gif" data-w="640" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 640px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagNomibLyq7biaIWa9kjwhwpxxUGJF0fUFiafOibGGt2G4ZY9whfPDHuwmiag/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">视频到视频编辑</span><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></strong><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">扩散模型激发了多种根据文本 prompt 编辑图像和视频的方法。OpenAI 的研究团队将其中一种方法 ——SDEdit 应用于 Sora，使得 Sora 能够在零样本（zero-shot）条件下改变输入视频的风格和环境。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">输入视频如下：</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="503424091" data-ratio="0.5625" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="800" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagueJUbCowjVvyYgYWGma26vCXibicgfaYKAzyE3ynAzCKvPVCvcM81FLg/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">输出结果：</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="503424092" data-ratio="0.5625" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="960" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagdgG6SeOYARWCrtgbk8sLqdicMRLIIYZ4AKrKkWM9qlaPaiaCkkDfYdBA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">连接视频</span><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"></span></strong><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">我们还可以使用 Sora 在两个输入视频之间逐渐进行转场，从而在具有完全不同主题和场景构成的视频之间创建无缝过渡。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="503424097" data-ratio="0.5625" data-type="gif" data-w="800" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiag20uhDe5WhxjNicHXjaBdcloFE30Lq0WV3YnzVz8RXSWAJY5upicWTy4Q/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="503424095" data-ratio="0.5625" data-type="gif" data-w="960" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagPLA9KjIaRrdP68M0tBSib5kCENrbgWoBlic24R0jcbWulqTyuWftEpjQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;">图像生成能力</strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">Sora 还能生成图像。为此，OpenAI 将高斯噪声 patch 排列在空间网格中，时间范围为一帧。该模型可生成不同大小的图像，最高分辨率可达 2048x2048。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="503424093" data-ratio="1.137037037037037" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagYXQRMxQgKzVcgsMvPW27WG1y1DKGDyia4cW2mBFicWbjUA1LGjiabTvkg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;">涌现模拟能力</strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">OpenAI 发现，视频模型在经过大规模训练后，会表现出许多有趣的新能力。这些能力使 Sora 能够模拟物理世界中的人、动物和环境的某些方面。这些特性的出现没有任何明确的三维、物体等归纳偏差 — 它们纯粹是规模现象。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">三维一致性。Sora 可以生成动态摄像机运动的视频。随着摄像机的移动和旋转，人物和场景元素在三维空间中的移动是一致的。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="503424096" data-ratio="0.5625" data-type="gif" data-w="800" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiags9b7eEHG9TgkQOfDBwAtgHUOuicx5syk0iaEKQoYYKL4euASU7adZhOw/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">长序列连贯性和目标持久性。视频生成系统面临的一个重大挑战是在对长视频进行采样时保持时间一致性。OpenAI 发现，虽然 Sora 并不总是能有效地模拟短距离和长距离的依赖关系，但它在很多时候仍然能做到这一点。例如，即使人、动物和物体被遮挡或离开画面，Sora 模型也能保持它们的存在。同样，它还能在单个样本中生成同一角色的多个镜头，并在整个视频中保持其外观。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="503424094" data-ratio="0.5625" data-type="gif" data-w="960" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagzkOKx35U5n4zyjhQD1ibCnrLpwMOdZ41d7W6SmYnNN2icrQ2XMtjL68g/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">与世界互动。Sora 有时可以模拟以简单方式影响世界状态的动作。例如，画家可以在画布上留下新的笔触，这些笔触会随着时间的推移而持续，或者一个人可以吃汉堡并留下咬痕。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="503424099" data-ratio="0.5625" data-type="gif" data-w="800" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagjZpMuSxM1jXyo98LRoVhbEdJxKjhziaERmQxthuO6UnMnBgTMz23lTQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">模拟数字世界。Sora 还能模拟人工进程，视频游戏就是一个例子。Sora 可以通过基本策略同时控制 Minecraft 中的玩家，同时高保真地呈现世界及其动态。只需在 Sora 的提示字幕中提及 「Minecraft」，就能零样本激发这些功能。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="503424101" data-ratio="0.5625" data-type="gif" data-w="800" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagmYT7KmwVlRYodursqmZOJTFicdFcMq6ibWDfFxjGVDl7iaXjuSCRYehbA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">这些功能表明，视频模型的持续扩展是开发物理和数字世界以及其中的物体、动物和人的高能力模拟器的一条大有可为的道路。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;">局限性讨论</strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">作为一款模拟器，Sora 目前还存在许多局限性。例如，它不能准确模拟许多基本交互的物理现象，如玻璃碎裂。其他交互，如吃食物，并不总能产生正确的物体状态变化。官方主页列举了该模型的其他常见失效模式，例如长时间样本中出现的不一致性或物体的自发出现。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="503424098" data-ratio="0.5633333333333334" data-type="gif" data-w="600" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 600px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiagwNjUCs4m8D7LVqn7R1SpYliaqyoJEvzUiag0S8uibNg5bAWJ9kZjKuqZg/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="503424100" data-ratio="0.75" data-type="gif" data-w="640" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 640px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/KmXPKA19gW912jYqObuUwSCOibjYChBiag9yzDgu2iaItXXElZxUYa3KCZxOQZJBzfFfDU3zIlpC39PUtRZDtULvA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;">不过，Sora 目前所展现的能力证明了持续扩大视频模型的规模是一个充满希望的方向，这也将助力物理和数字世界及其中的物体、动物和人类能够有更加精确的模拟。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">更多详细内容，请参阅 Sora 原始技术报告。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><br style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;"><em style="outline: 0px;">参考链接：https://openai.com/research/video-generation-models-as-world-simulators</em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><br></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="578" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="645" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="503424102" data-ratio="0.8305555555555556" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="height: 480px;width: 578px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/KmXPKA19gW9BcwDFz901ZX0iaIEk07W0Q6SZr9pu0tfoIelKhoSSymoOjB3PbKtjqiaiarOibX8GTCnRWwfO2ehVibQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><br></p><p class="mp_profile_iframe_wrp"><mp-common-profile class="js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe" data-pluginname="mpprofile" data-id="MzkwODI4NjY2Mw==" data-headimg="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/bTicW6huibprLhW8WYM5M1CENXBd7Xn3bIjaTia6BX9cRhZ4ic6YHCDrv4ec9ao4tbtd6YEy7E9zCiascIEZzsEWibAA/0?wx_fmt=png" data-nickname="机器之心PRO会员" data-alias="almosthuman2014pro" data-signature="一份让您从此不再担心因业务繁忙而错失AI &amp; Robotics 赛道良机的业内通讯" data-from="0" data-is_biz_ban="0"></mp-common-profile></p><p mp-original-font-size="17" mp-original-line-height="27.200000762939453" style="margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 0px;text-wrap: wrap;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);text-size-adjust: auto;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;line-height: 27.2px;"><span mp-original-font-size="12" mp-original-line-height="19.200000762939453" style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 19.2px;">©&nbsp;THE END&nbsp;</span></p><p mp-original-font-size="17" mp-original-line-height="27.200000762939453" style="margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 0px;text-wrap: wrap;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);text-size-adjust: auto;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;line-height: 27.2px;"><span mp-original-font-size="12" mp-original-line-height="19.200000762939453" style="outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);line-height: 19.2px;">转载请联系本公众号获得授权</span></p><p mp-original-font-size="17" mp-original-line-height="27.200000762939453" style="margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 0px;text-wrap: wrap;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);text-size-adjust: auto;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;line-height: 27.2px;"><span mp-original-font-size="12" mp-original-line-height="19.200000762939453" style="outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);line-height: 19.2px;">投稿或寻求报道：content@jiqizhixin.com</span></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="10000"></mp-style-type></p>]]></summary>
